# Gmail
IMAPStore gmail-remote
Host imap.gmail.com
SSLType IMAPS
AuthMechs LOGIN
User jiro.due@gmail.com
Pass "stfo tcoc mfhp mliz"

MaildirStore gmail-local
Path ~/Mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/Mail/gmail/INBOX/
Subfolders Verbatim

#IMAPAccount gmail
#Account gmail

Channel gmail
Master :gmail-remote:
Slave :gmail-local:
Patterns *
Create Slave
SyncState *
Expunge Both
 
